						<div class='m-0'><p class='font-bold text-sm lg:text-justify mb-2 sm:mb-3'>ACCESS YOUR GROWTH METRICS</p>
						<p>Access a visual depiction of your achievement over time by taking advantage of Milestone's graphical features to generate charts and metrics of your progress.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class='col-start-2 col-end-12 bsm:col-start-7 bsm:col-end-12 lg:col-start-7 lg:col-end-10 flex flex-col'>
					<div class='flex mb-2'>
						<div class='m-0'><p class='font-bold text-sm lg:text-justifymb-2 sm:mb-3'>REPORT GENERATION</p>
						<p>Not only can you view and track your achievements and note worthy accomplishments. You can also generate hard copy reports for display and use elsewhere.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>	
